/>\n喺 Zurich 坐 Regonal Express 向Chur方向嘅火車，無記錯個零鐘就到<br />\n值得一提嘅係沿途風光好靚，遇著好天真係正到不得了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個車站側邊有個巴士站，無記錯坐11號車就直達首都<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/29/074617_24dc4edddf5590de99048b6be45ae989.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2F074617_24dc4edddf5590de99048b6be45ae989.JPG&h=fab3b779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上有嘢睇嘅只係首都嗰條街，有郵票博物館，國會大廈，手信舖，餐廳嗰啲<br />\n真係叫做打張卡，揼個印仔落passport（喺旅客中心俾錢揼），同寄下明信片之外冇乜好做<br />\n<br />\n利申：舊年去過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/29/075046_99eadf8dcbacf12e23fbab537e1b946d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2F075046_99eadf8dcbacf12e23fbab537e1b946d.JPG&h=f2e24e2e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}